{"title":"13. Urticaria","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/MKSAP - 18/Dermatología/13. Urticaria.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Urticaria","guid":"DBK8J-JWrTholmMyf-KdXQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"General ","guid":"IPwNoO8Dzl3TqWDV7vHAEA","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"degranulación de mastocitos y la liberación de proteínas inflamatorias,\\Ncomo histamina, leucotrienos, complemento y prostaglandinas","guid":"JD1w2a7a6NHgThxP61UZUA","children":[]}]},{"id":"3","parent":"0","text":"Clinica ","guid":"u1P_dlxDGRHdiAE-tr5fSQ","children":[{"id":"4","parent":"3","text":"placas eritematosas bien demarcadas","guid":"I7ijaXIGmN9HxM3NEECRMA","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"aparecer en áreas corporales sometidas a presión o\\Nfrotamiento repetitivos, como la cintura y la nuca","guid":"9_kFX65ybnZQSOlV55uRGQ","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"4","text":"lesiones individuales pueden ser eritematosas o\\Nblancas, rodeadas a menudo por un halo rojo","guid":"5qUq0s1MYumMuZBNCVtMqw","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"4","text":"diversidad de formas, como redonda, oval,\\Nanular, arciforme o serpiginosa","guid":"E53eHMbInX6xYgm6iCwJEA","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"4","text":"centro de la lesión es normalmente piel\\Nclara o rosada blanqueable.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"4","text":"tamaño de 1-8 cm","guid":"PbZ1xsrJZ7cQSQeawMjfZA","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"4","text":"extremadamente pruriginosas","guid":"XMwi9jiV9MSWXFFLgupN4Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"11","parent":"3","text":"Urticaria aguda","guid":"","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"desarrollan rápidamente y se\\Nresuelven en cuestión de horas","guid":"yoaNCXzspkSqCpmMmZYswg","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"deberían resolverse en menos de 24 horas, los brotes\\Nrecurrentes de habones pueden durar varias semanas","guid":"efkHxOpkitPNqk7bgqljgg","children":[]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"11","text":"mayoría de los casos de urticaria se resuelve\\Nespontáneamente, y la causa nunca llega a determinarse","guid":"8uz9eeiSWRy7eZR9oYY7jw","children":[]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"3","text":"urticaria crónica","guid":"rwmpWWgdSqs55wc8AdSMHQ","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"episodios duran más de seis semanas","guid":"7wd_BWtpu3HZL8ZpEjo5fw","children":[]}]},{"id":"17","parent":"3","text":"vasculitis urticarial\\NSospechar si","guid":"JCiUMLaT2Z4FpT8jfIFycw","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"lesiones urticariales individuales no se resuelven después de 24 horas","guid":"e8vDTpJZ0t2ZKARrZgYqLQ","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"acompañan de síntomas sistémicos (dolor articular, fiebre)","guid":"YjRzPRAQF8biy_qB3JkWqg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"0","text":"diagnóstico de\\Nurticaria es clínico","guid":"v5NtDftYQBzVdzd0rmjLMA","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"maniobras físicas que pueden\\Ncoadyuvar al diagnóstico","guid":"JxRJsXmfD3-xtowLrlQtXA","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"cercar las lesiones y ver si se han\\Nresuelto al cabo de 24 horas","guid":"4Cy1jtpL_rMU-ANZY3NPiA","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"21","text":"raspar suavemente piel indemne con el extremo de\\Nmadera de un depresor lingual y ver si se induce urticaria","guid":"70KueFBfaUWqD-FCIa_QFg","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"dermatografismo","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"25","parent":"20","text":"causa\\Nanamnesis y la exploración física","guid":"29plTXQLG0Z5AjD_bhijLA","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"urticaria aguda\\Nen adultos","guid":"SHZUii3xLQWwMQvwJP4y-w","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"causas más comunes","guid":"","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"infecciones virales y las\\Nreacciones farmacológicas","guid":"AshtqDuAkXqZmc3qVGlnZQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"26","text":"reacciones alérgicas inducidas por\\Nalimentos pueden ser intensas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"mariscos, cacahuetes y frutos secos","guid":"g_o9AZM3B-lYivVyRVip0g","children":[]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"26","text":"Otras causas inusuales","guid":"","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"enfermedad tiroidea autoinmune","guid":"RWdgX4RwNMjQQcSnyw8VqA","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"31","text":"neoplasias malignas","guid":"YfLxuXXTyoLx2gfQKzJWTg","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"linfoma","guid":"Bmy7EqxTMIVNunMWaEFk2w","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"25","text":"urticaria\\Nfísica","guid":"IGLoz9gvB-qwaZfuZcI57Q","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"inducida por un estímulo físico","guid":"76T0aDgRoO8BTP9prvo12g","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"35","text":"luz solar, sudoración, presión física,\\Nvibración, agua o temperatura fría","guid":"bQYv-o7exD-Zm9bPiVmLHw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"38","parent":"20","text":"evaluación\\Ndiagnóstica","guid":"N1CqNY3_8Kwhl66_A49hbw","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"No se recomienda","guid":"Jyn7GnBTR2-rq38Uji50EA","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"a menos que la anamnesis sugiera una causa específica","guid":"sLzBQo1Stb85_TXy4ssRzQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"38","text":"síntomas persisten","guid":"ZFJvtPi4QPGgNLrw0zDT_A","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"pruebas de laboratorio, que incluyen hemograma completo con fórmula leucocitaria, análisis de orina,\\Nvelocidad de sedimentación globular o proteína C reactiva, tirotropina (TSH) y bioquímica hepática.","guid":"zqg0bW-OIa0rIyUmxyuj8w","children":[]}]},{"id":"43","parent":"38","text":"síntomas sistémicos o se sospecha vasculitis urticarial,\\Ndeberían considerarse pruebas guiadas por los hallazgos","guid":"1xsBRgev47jSPj8H2_cHuw","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"vasculitis urticarial","guid":"wSsr1xgQ-wl4hagFEkTr0w","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"lesiones dolorosas o urentes","guid":"vP9UUlDYXk8mtNDgZTyrzg","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"44","text":"deja cambios parecidos a hematomas cuando se resuelve","guid":"iKYpzBOi1mfULNeiED68EQ","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"44","text":"tienen con frecuencia una\\Nenfermedad autoinmune subyacente","guid":"Fk7HGzDL-eIfMgXqPouNhw","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"lupus eritematoso","guid":"PAMO8oUeR8WpAS6OBKeuNw","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"47","text":"dolor articular","guid":"jZIt_kn14C1JfKwIpc7V4w","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"44","text":"corren riesgo de\\Nenfermedad multisistémica","guid":"s1ZZed3BlkD6qkW-0oxAHQ","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"sobre todo vasculitis urticarial hipocomplementémica","guid":"Ou560yRr8RHOM0_wInZQzQ","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"50","text":"p. ej., nefritis","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"id":"53","parent":"20","text":"biopsia cutánea","guid":"MmlPHhcvm5oek9k-RUp1kw","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"útil para diagnosticar vasculitis urticarial y debería considerarse en pacientes con\\Nlesiones dolorosas, síntomas sistémicos o lesiones individuales persistentes","guid":"CL33dOha3xervpVDBdy2aw","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"53","text":"biopsia de piel convencional (para histología) y una biopsia para inmunofluorescencia\\Ndirecta (con el fin de detectar depósitos de inmunoglobulinas y complemento)","guid":"yu57-Upee3BsMiZ7fcv1Kg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"56","parent":"0","text":"angioedema","guid":"l6lqCHg5x0OBg3-0DyBfmw","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"General ","guid":"C_RDo_t-02-H5XXUgGeSiQ","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"forma subcutánea o submucosa de urticaria","guid":"Y11eHTT3tor_e9hOjvxmVQ","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"57","text":"extravasación de líquido hacia\\Nlos tejidos intersticiales","guid":"-8sy7xKC2YGDuLw60GaYpw","children":[]}]},{"id":"60","parent":"56","text":"Clinica ","guid":"","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"transitoria y localizada","guid":"dFQ40QzmEm6KDKD4iFqrRQ","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"60","text":"puede aparecer con o sin urticaria","guid":"kGrddGSwdwnv2CPw3iP0wg","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"60","text":"angioedema que afecta a la cara y las\\Nvías aéreas es una emergencia","guid":"5exX_HT5FDMwQFaUY9kvBg","children":[]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"56","text":"Tratamiento ","guid":"4dW_LmC1KJ-VZh5CR62Wkw","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"adrenalina sistémica y\\Nglucocorticoides","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"66","parent":"0","text":"angioedema\\Nhereditario","guid":"AT8cHU7n_P6rUaRb48VoZg","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"General ","guid":"MIhfQen5q780bTCYPoazIg","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"distinto del angioedema más típico asociado a mastocitos","guid":"iR7vXSOeQqZ3SCyUKFnX8A","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"causado por la activación de la cascada del complemento como\\Nconsecuencia de la falta o disfunción del inhibidor de la esterasa C1","guid":"Y3KiYgGTvTvr8STuUu4chw","children":[]}]},{"id":"70","parent":"66","text":"Clinica ","guid":"gljZ1xqCxqAxaj82rCB8cQ","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"edema localizado esporádico que\\Nafecte a la cabeza y cuello","guid":"QGnGsajke4jmhZ6MYfnffg","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"70","text":"ausencia de lesiones urticariales típicas","guid":"KxD4lyMygQcUuwLZ1hzCwg","children":[]}]},{"id":"73","parent":"66","text":"diagnóstico","guid":"Q4eE_A5ipHRWq_kCr9THjw","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"determinando los niveles cuantitativos y funcionales del\\Ninhibidor de la esterasa C1 y los niveles de complemento C4.","guid":"8J1iZb7iaPTEvMS8FYvnbw","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":74,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Dermatología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/MKSAP - 18/Dermatología","filename":"13. Urticaria","id":"map_1208","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"13. Urticaria"}